comment: * Interface used to report status of taking screenshot.

methods.name: void onSuccess(@NonNull ScreenshotResult screenshot)
methods.comment:
Called when taking screenshot has completed successfully.
         *
         * @param screenshot The content of screenshot.

methods.name: void onFailure(@ScreenshotErrorCode int errorCode)
methods.comment:
Called when taking screenshot has failed. {@code errorCode} will identify the
         * reason of failure.
         *
         * @param errorCode The error code of this operation.
